    \subsubsection{Account Related Functional Requirements}

    \begin{enumerate}
        \item The program should allow a new user to create a new account. 
              The user will have to provide a valid and unique username. A valid password and a personal phone number. 
              \begin{itemize}
                \item [-] Input: A valid username, a valid password, a valid phone number, a first name, and a last name.
                \item [-] Output: Creation of a new account.
                \item [-] Constraints: The username should not be longer than 20 characters. 
                      The password should contain at least: One number, one lowercase letter, and one uppercase letter. 
                      The phone number should be valid.                  
                \item [-] Priority: Mo; must have.
              \end{itemize}
    \end{enumerate}
